Microsoft Windows:
------------------
* Microft Visual C++ 6.0
 - Open workspace file in /troll/build/msw/msvc6 and compile 
   it will generate some libs under /troll/lib/vc6_lib (troll_base(d).lib , troll_allegro(d).lib, troll_sdl(d).lib)
   
* Microft Visual C++ 2005
 - Open workspace file in /troll/build/msw/msvc8 and compile 
   it will generate some libs under /troll/lib/vc8_lib (troll_base(d).lib , troll_allegro(d).lib, troll_sdl(d).lib)
   
Microsoft Windows Mobile/Windows CE
------------------
* Microft Visual C++ 2005
 - Open workspace file in /troll/build/msw/msvc8 and compile (change the build configuration to Pocket PC)
   it will generate some libs under /troll/lib/vc8_lib_arm4 (troll_base(d).lib , troll_allegro(d).lib, troll_sdl(d).lib)
   
Mac OS X
-----------------
* Xcode
 - Open project at /troll/build/mac/troll.xcodeproj and compile it.
 - Open project at /troll/modules/sdl/build/mac/troll_sdl.xcodeproj and compile it (to use SDL module)
 - Open project at /troll/modules/allegro/build/mac/troll_allegro.xcodeproj and compile it (to use Allegro module)   

For Allegro support you need the following libraries installed:
* Allegro	http://alleg.sourceforge.net/

For SDL support you need the following libraries installed:
* SDL		http://www.libsdl.org



